                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/871" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0147</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9317 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒安标准人寿打造中国首个寿险指数</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HASL Founded the first insurance index In China</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李桂华，卢宏亮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南开大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒安标准人寿有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒安标准人寿；人寿保险；指数营销；2012百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HASL; Life insurance; Index Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2007年9月18日，恒安标准人寿有限公司与南开大学合作研发并无偿发布了保险行业的首个寿险指数，此后该指数每年连续发布。该指数的每一次发布都引起各大媒体对寿险指数和恒安标准人寿公司的广泛关注。恒安标准寿险指数的第一大亮点在于将客户的需求“指数化”，用“寿险指数”的形式反映消费者的认知水平，并对研究成果加以运用，对客户进行指数营销。恒安寿险指数的第二大亮点在于，该指数首次在量化分析的基础上引入典型人群定性访谈，描摹国人“险商”。几年的积累使得恒安标准寿险指数不仅在业界和消费者群中颇具说服力和影响力，实现了差异化营销，而且恒安标准寿险指数的相关成果也不断地被恒安标准人寿应用于寿险产品和服务的研发工作中，并取得了很好的营销绩效。任何理论成果只有真正用于实践才能使它的价值最大化，而恒安标准寿险指数就是这样一个成功的典范。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On September 18th, 2007, Heng An Standard Life Insurance Co.,Ltd（HASL）and Nankai University conducted research cooperatively and released gratuitously the first insurance index in the field of insurance in China; since then the insurance index has been released annually. Every release of the insurance index had caused major Medias’ widespread attention to the index and HASL. The first major highlight of Heng An Standard Insurance Index (HASII) is the indexation of the customers&#39; needs, and it reflected the level of consumers’ awareness in the form of &quot;insurance index&quot;, simultaneously, the HASII has been used in daily operations for customer development and index marketing of HASL . The second bright spot of HASII is that the index introduced “qualitative interview of typical crowd” according to people’s “risk quotient” on the basis of quantitative analysis for the first time. In a few years time, HASII not only has played major role and become the most persuasive and influential benchmarking tool of the whole insurance industry in achieving a differentiated marketing efforts, but in the continuously research and development of the new products and services in achieving remarkable marketing performance as well. This shows that any theoretical results can achieve the maximum value only by applying the theory into practice, and HASII is such a successful model.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《服务营销》、《市场营销概论》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销战略 顾客导向、产品差异化、营销沟通</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-09</td>
